{"tid":2133648,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"馬蹄露有幾賤？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-07-31T08:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T08:37:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3de656a65f29112d5cec3de46edb106c56e1bb8c","tid":2133648,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/6L5XFQCAPNGHXEX4XAMA2LP2VY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2F6L5XFQCAPNGHXEX4XAMA2LP2VY%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG14jkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=e57b3563\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2F6L5XFQCAPNGHXEX4XAMA2LP2VY%2F&h=3ad06dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/6L5XFQCAPNGHXEX4XAMA2LP2VY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露有幾賤？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tQhobaufe2GQBDMMAI14DaZ2kbw=/1205x1328/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5XPFTY7VWFAIBMMBA3JSXEACFQ.jPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtQhobaufe2GQBDMMAI14DaZ2kbw%3D%2F1205x1328%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5XPFTY7VWFAIBMMBA3JSXEACFQ.jPG&h=e02ee4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天時運低，見人分享藍。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本欄六月七日已月旦。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n以我觀察，像馬蹄露這樣想的下愚藍絲也有不少。此等藍絲會說，不能漠視他人利益及生命，卻絕口不提陷港人於險地的，正是近月對三十三類人（尤其是海員）豁免強制檢疫，人為擴大病毒缺口的特區政府。反觀台灣，年初當機立斷封關後，疫情早就受控，現在台灣人已可不戴口罩在夜市從容「掃街」。<br />\n<br />\n當然，按馬蹄露的邏輯，禁堂食的香港其實就是一個遍地開花的大型台灣夜市；可以一邊抗疫一邊掃街，香港人應該很高興。但對心智正常人來說，把草根人士大汗淋漓、冒着風雨跪在街頭吃飯，跟市民平日「掃街」吃喝之樂相提並論，不但比擬不倫，更是涼薄到極點。馬蹄露寫得出這樣賤的撐政府「理由」，屈健筆和「搣時潘」應該感到後浪的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n蠢物。。。。。。。。。。。北宋有個好講水利而急於求成的官員提議，不如把梁山泊八百里水域都改成農田，有人就問：「那麼梁山泊的水該排到哪裏？」出名博學而冷幽默的劉貢父聽見，即一本正經說：「在梁山泊旁邊鑿一個八百里的池，就可以接收排出來的水了。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n執筆時，政府忽然宣布取消「禁堂食令」，不知道馬蹄露會不會撰文斥責政府「妄顧」750萬人性命呢？"},{"pid":"44d56446b34c665015820d53ed0e5041fa68b7d8","tid":2133648,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題<br />\n馬蹄露有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060c159284865769e47cef33467989111c921e48","tid":2133648,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d56446b34c665015820d53ed0e5041fa68b7d8","tid":2133648,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題<br />\n馬蹄露有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33883ee174478f50ef5b195b21554d54dc184d37","tid":2133648,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44d56446b34c665015820d53ed0e5041fa68b7d8","tid":2133648,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題<br />\n馬蹄露有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"冇錯喎<br />\n有幾賤咪有幾錢"},{"pid":"a5bd1190e6ed8488225bffcd8f4bf8c349d60c57","tid":2133648,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f35be32c3935751fa68502be9a08ec70ee4101","tid":2133648,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44d56446b34c665015820d53ed0e5041fa68b7d8","tid":2133648,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題<br /